definition.value: A N(5)-alkylglutamine where the alkyl group is ethyl. It has been isolated from green tea.
A member of the class of oxindoles that is oxindole (1,3-dihydro-2H-indol-2-one) in which one of the hydrogens at position 3 has been replaced by a methyl group.
A polymer composed of repeating 2-(N-acetyl-D-glucosaminyl)ribitol 1-phosphate units.
